      "Subaortic stenosis (SAS) — congenital cardiac condition; cardiac auscultation by a board-certified cardiologist on every puppy is the breed-club recommendation.",
      "Hypothyroidism + autoimmune disorders — over-represented; annual bloodwork.",
      "Heat stroke — heavy black double coat absorbs heat fast. Above 75°F is uncomfortable, above 85°F dangerous. Cooling vests, indoor exercise, never leaving them in cars.",
